item.title: CVE-2021-21573|2024-08-03T18:16:23.393Z -- dell -- biosconnect
item.description: Dell BIOSConnect feature contains a buffer overflow vulnerability. An authenticated malicious admin user with local access to the system may potentially exploit this vulnerability to run arbitrary code and bypass UEFI restrictions.
